	<h2>Humpty Dumpty rhyme pack</h2>


	<p>Build up a collection of resources based on a nursery rhyme and keep them together in a pack such as a zipped plastic wallet or an attractive drawstring bag. Use these packs with the children in your setting, or set up a ‘lending scheme’ to encourage parents to share the rhymes with their children at home.</p>


	<p>In the pack, include a &#8220;copy of the nursery rhyme&#8221;; Humpty Dumpty puppet; set of magnetic character pieces created by cutting out &#8220;pictures of the characters&#8221; or the children’s drawings, laminating them and attaching magentic tape to the back; Come Alive Nursery Rhymes wooden character set; ‘Humpty Dumpty’ rhyme.</p>
